subSubSection.paragraph:
Previous records : Bergen and Stavanger ( Burton, 1930b ; as
L. macleayi
); Singlefjord ( Breitfuss, 1936 ).

The species is also reported from the Mediterranean ( Von Lendenfeld, 1891 ), the Bay of Biscay down to 550 m depth ( Borojevic & Boury-Esnault, 1987 ), Great Britain (
Ackers et al ., 1985
) and the Arctic ( Breitfuss, 1911 , 1927 , 1933 ; Derjugin, 1915 ).
